{"id":"es-320","language":"spanish","category_slug":"spanish-intermediate","category_name":"Spanish Listening - Intermediate","position":320,"title":"320. ¿Cuál es tu animal favorito?","subtitle":"Daniel / Chile","level":"Intermediate Spanish","parts":8,"url":"https://www.spanishlistening.org/content/320-daniel-animal.html","audio_url":"","youtube_video_id":"","vimeo_video_id":"101369458","video_url":"//player.vimeo.com/video/101369458?title=0&byline=0","details_cached_at":"2026-06-29T13:54:21","challenges":[{"position":1,"content":"La pregunta es:","audio_url":"","time_start":null,"time_end":null},{"position":2,"content":"¿Cuál es tu animal favorito?","audio_url":"","time_start":null,"time_end":null},{"position":3,"content":"La verdad es que mi animal favorito son las focas.","audio_url":"","time_start":null,"time_end":null},{"position":4,"content":"Sí, las focas. Porque creo que son impresionantes.","audio_url":"","time_start":null,"time_end":null},{"position":5,"content":"Me encanta cómo las focas pueden jugar con una pelota, siendo que no las tienen en su ambiente natural y cómo son tan buenas jugando con pelotas.","audio_url":"","time_start":null,"time_end":null},{"position":6,"content":"Eso me encanta de ellas.","audio_url":"","time_start":null,"time_end":null},{"position":7,"content":"Y todo lo que pueden hacer en el agua, su forma... no sé, se ven demasiado tiernas.","audio_url":"","time_start":null,"time_end":null},{"position":8,"content":"Por eso, la foca es mi animal favorito.","audio_url":"","time_start":null,"time_end":null}]}